items.title: Awesome Pyramid
items.content_text:
### Other

*   [pyramid\_pages (⭐12)](https://github.com/uralbash/pyramid_pages) - Provides a
    collections of tree pages to your Pyramid application. This is very similar
    to django.contrib.flatpages but with a tree structure and traversal algorithm
    in URL dispatch.
items.content_html:
Other

  • pyramid_pages (⭐12) - Provides a collections of tree pages to your Pyramid application. This is very similar to django.contrib.flatpages but with a tree structure and traversal algorithm in URL dispatch.
